      "id": "01a22933_caa8af19",
      "file_path": "policyhandler/pdp_api/DMaap/Subscriber.py",
      "patchset_number": 4,
      "line": 50,
      "message": "1. would it be useful to provide timeout and limit for the query to DMaaP MR ?\nhttps://wiki.onap.org/display/DW/DMaaP+API\n\n2. should the timeouts and other params come from config.json or discoverable config coming from consul-kv instead of being hardcoded ?\n\n3. why do you quote after joining the url with the path ?\n\n4. are you loosing all '/'s here ?\n   https://docs.python.org/3/library/urllib.parse.html#urllib.parse.quote_plus \n   quote_plus('/El Niño/') yields '%2FEl+Ni%C3%B1o%2F'\n>>> url = urllib.parse.urljoin('http://my-hostname:1234', 'events/aviral/ph/5678')\n>>> url\n'http://my-hostname:1234/events/aviral/ph/5678'\n>>> url2 = urllib.parse.quote_plus(url, safe='')\n>>> url2\n'http%3A%2F%2Fmy-hostname%3A1234%2Fevents%2Faviral%2Fph%2F5678'\n\n5. did you test this ?",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 1949,
